This dataset includes the data needed to reproduce Minard's famous
"Napoleon's Russian Campaign" visualization from 1869.  The data was
captured from
https://www.datavis.ca/gallery/minard/ggplot2/ggplot2-minard-gallery.zip
on Feb. 1 2022.  https://www.datavis.ca/gallery/re-minard.php provides
full context, including the "Re-Visions of Mard" software challenge.

To use this data, un-zip the archive and find the three included .txt file.
These can be parsed by pandas.read_csv(filename, delim_whitespace=True) .
